Xinhua News reporter Shang Rui reported: Recently, the atmospheric environment and bioenergy team of Tianjin University has made significant progress towards " carbon dioxide capture by membrane separation " and successfully developed a new type of mixed matrix membrane preparation technology, greatly improving the carbon dioxide capture performance of membrane materials.
