Large-scale financial media action " Go to the village live to see poverty alleviation " - first generation network - Zhengsheng online
New Hunan Client July 25 (This reporter) On July 25, the large-scale integrated media campaign " Go to the Village Live to See Poverty Alleviation, " sponsored by the Financial Program Center of Radio Central Television, started from Xuzhou, Jiangsu Province. Two caravans carrying 5G new media mobile cloud broadcasting system were seen by the on-site guests and slowly drove out of the scene.
General Secretary Xi Jinping pointed out, " 2020 is a landmark year. We will build a moderately prosperous society in all respects and achieve the first centennial goal. 2020 is also the year of the decisive battle for poverty eradication. "
The large-scale integrated media campaign " Go to the Village Live to Watch Poverty Alleviation " is an important measure taken by the Financial Programme Center of the Central Radio and Television Network to promote poverty alleviation in line with this major theme.
The action will go into poverty alleviation villages in more than 20 provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government, explore vivid stories of poverty alleviation, pay close attention to the great changes in the appearance of villages, and show how villagers can break through the difficulties of survival and development and move towards prosperity.
The operation will last more than three months.
Starting from Xuzhou, the soldiers divided into two routes, one way to the southwest line, passing through Anhui, Hubei, Jiangxi, Hunan, Guangxi, Guizhou, Sichuan, Chongqing, Yunnan, Tibet and other places; the other way to the northwest line, passing through Henan, Shaanxi, Gansu, Qinghai, Xinjiang, Ningxia, Inner Mongolia, Shanxi, Hebei and other places, with a journey of more than 10,000 kilometers.
In the reporting form, " Go to the village live to see poverty alleviation " bold integration.
The economic development of the villages visited by the caravans will be broadcast through CCTV Finance Channel, Yangguang Economic Voice, China Traffic Radio, and CCTV Finance New Media.
Among them, the live television broadcast will be completed mainly on the midday news program " World Finance " of the CCTV Finance Channel (first broadcast time: Monday to Sunday 12: 00-13: 00), and the golden news program " Economic Information Network " of the CCTV Finance Channel will set up a poverty alleviation reporting column (first broadcast time: Monday to Sunday 20: 30-21: 30).
Meanwhile, the caravan will conduct a one-hour live broadcast to each village visited on the CCTV financial client. By downloading the CCTV financial APP, viewers can watch the live broadcast and participate in the lucky draw.
In terms of technology application and studio design, " Go to the Village Live to Watch Poverty Alleviation " made a bold breakthrough and pioneered the " outfield new media caravan. "
The vehicle is equipped with a 5G new media mobile cloud broadcasting system and uses 5G + 4K / 8K + AI technology to realize the organic combination of online and offline, large and small screens, and television broadcasting.
It is equipped with a three-news broadcast area, which is converted from a container, which is 12 meters long, 2.55 meters wide and 3.98 meters high. The box adopts a hydraulic automatic expansion structure and can be turned up to 120 degrees.
The broadcast area can also be expanded automatically, and the external expansion platform covers an area of more than 50 square meters, which can meet the scene requirements of most programs.
At present, the Dongchuan District of Kunming is already hot in summer, and what is hotter than the weather is the pro-poor workshop next to the relocation settlement.
Lu Ling, an employee of Kunming Esford Electronic Technology, said, " Now, when you leave home, you enter the factory door and make money to take care of your family, thanks to the free vocational skills training provided by the trade union organization. "
Walking into the Dongchuan District Tongdu Street electronic components processing poverty alleviation workshop, a lively busy picture came into sight.
Lü Ling, in her 40s, is a single mother with her children alone and takes care of her elderly parents.
In her most difficult time, the Dongchuan District Federation of Trade Unions helped to come up with ideas and ways to " deliver coal in the snow " after running busy.
Since 2018, Lü Ling has enjoyed assistance policies such as housing, schooling, social security and employment, as well as assistance funds granted by trade unions at all levels.
This year, her child has successfully graduated and found employment. She also got a job and income after taking part in skills training, and was released from poverty at the end of April.
It is reported that the Dongchuan District General Organization's special skills training project to help alleviate poverty is part of the skills training work of the Yunnan Provincial Federation of Trade Unions.
Taking into account the characteristics of the difficult workers in the pro-poor relocation and resettlement sites in the area, the District General Administration has conducted an in-depth investigation to understand the training needs and determine the types of training. In the near future, it plans to train a total of 450 electricians, welders, face decorators, etc.
Recently, Li Yi, an employee of the Agricultural Bank of Yunnan Menglian County Branch, wrote a sincere thank-you letter to the County Federation of Trade Unions.
In her letter, she sincerely thanked the trade union for giving her golden autumn education money from August 2013 to January 2017 to help her complete her studies.
In 2004, Li Yi's father died in a car accident, and her mother was included in the files of workers in difficulty. Since then, she has enjoyed the care of the policy.
With the help of the local trade union, Li Yi successfully completed her studies.
Since 2016, 3,809 households have been lifted out of poverty through institutional guarantees and precise assistance.
The successful relief of Lü Ling's family and Li Yi is a microcosm of the work of Yunnan trade unions to promote the relief of workers in difficulty.
According to Duan Kaiyuan, a staff member of the Legal and Human Rights Work Department of the Yunnan Provincial Federation of Trade Unions, the province has strengthened the dynamic management of the files of workers in difficulty, promoted the normalization of file-building work, and promptly integrated the workers in difficulty who meet the conditions for file-building into the assistance system; broadened the application channels for workers in difficulty, and opened an online file-building service platform for workers in difficulty using WeChat to make it easier for workers in difficulty to declare on their own initiative in a timely manner.
During the epidemic, it was difficult to go out to work. In order to help workers in difficulty alleviate the pressure of their lives, Yunnan Province arranged a total of more than 13 million yuan to send warm funds, and carried out special warm sympathy activities to more than 6,000 households at the national level and more than 1,000 households at the provincial level, in accordance with the standards of 2,000 yuan per household for workers in difficulty at the national level and 1,500 yuan per household for workers in difficulty at the provincial level.
At the same time, the Provincial General Administration connects with various Internet recruitment platforms such as social security departments and smart union recruitment, pushes recruitment information to workers in difficulty, and provides employment consultation, employment guidance and other services.
